\f0\b\fs40 \cf0 Death to Selfie
\f1\b0\fs24 \uc0\u8232 Week 1 \'96 My prayer should be your prayer\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 INTRO\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}My hope and prayer for this next series is that God would wreck you in a great way.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Modern simple narcissistic Christianity isn\'92t working\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The New York Times had an article this week that talked about the decline in people who associate with Christianity \'96 8% in 7 years!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God calls us to a higher life and higher standard than many of us are living right now\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Today we\'92re going to look at 7 questions that come from the first few verses\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 GOD\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 1\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 Paul, an apostle\'a0of Christ Jesus by the will of God,\'a0and Timothy\'a0our brother,\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 2\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub To God\'92s holy people in Colossae, the faithful brothers and sisters
\fs15 \super [\ul a\ulnone ]
\fs24 \nosupersub \'a0in Christ:\
Grace\'a0and peace to you from God our Father.
\fs15 \super [\ul b\ulnone ]\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf0 \nosupersub {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Every person needs both Grace and Peace and neither can be attained from ourselves but only God.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 3\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 \nosupersub We always thank God,\'a0the Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, when we pray for you, \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Not sure what to do with this verse?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 4\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub because we have heard of your faith in Christ Jesus and of the love\'a0you have for all God\'92s people\'97\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Real quick \'96 if someone were to hear about your faith in God and how much you love other people \'96 would they be thankful or confused by it?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Our culture is so confused by Christians not because of their theology but because of their actions.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 5\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub the faith and love that spring from the hope\'a0stored up for you in heaven and about which you have already heard in the true message\'a0of the gospel\'a0
\f0\b\fs18 \super 6\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub that has come to you.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There are two things that motivate Christians and depending on which one motivates you determines your outward grace level.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The first is stuff \'96 My hope is based on the stuff that God can give me \'96 health and wealth \'96 prosperity gospel\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Narcissistic Christianity \'96 here and now\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This works great until it doesn\'92t.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You are nice to people as long as they are nice to you.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You give to God as long as God is giving to you\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You pray to God as long as what you are asking you are getting.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Many Christians either walk away from God completely or just pragmatically because \'93It doesn\'92t work\'94.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The other is because of what is coming in the end.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You are living LIFE \'96 Living Intentionally For Eternity!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}These people\'92s relationship with God is much more stable and even keel.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs28 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What compels you in life?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 In the same way, the gospel is bearing fruit\'a0and growing throughout the whole world\'97just as it has been doing among you since the day you heard it and truly understood God\'92s grace.\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I want to pause here for a moment and say something that is very important.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Your works do not give you salvation but they reveal it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can\'92t earn your salvation by what you do but what do exposes the salvation that you have received.  \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs28 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What fruit do you have in your life right now?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs18 \cf2 \super 7\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub You learned it from Epaphras,\'a0our dear fellow servant,
\fs15 \super [\ul c\ulnone ]
\fs24 \nosupersub \'a0who is a faithful minister\'a0of Christ on our
\fs15 \super [\ul d\ulnone ]
\fs24 \nosupersub \'a0behalf,\'a0
\f0\b\fs18 \super 8\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub and who also told us of your love in the Spirit.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs28 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Do people talk about how loving you are or something else?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs18 \cf2 \super 9\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub For this reason, since the day we heard about you,\'a0we have not stopped praying for you. \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What Reason?  That They became Christians.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He hasn\'92t stop praying for two things \'96 thanksgiving of what God has done in their lives is the first\'85Here is the second\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 We continually ask God to fill you with the knowledge of his will\'a0through all the wisdom and understanding that the Spirit gives,\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is not enough to become a Christian\'85you now have a job!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92ve been recruited!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Too often we stop and think I\'92m a Christian, now I\'92m going back to my life or somehow it is an ad on to what I already have\'85it\'92s not.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs28 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Who wins between your will or God\'92s?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs18 \cf2 \super 10\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub so that you may live a life worthy\'a0of the Lord and please him\'a0in every way:\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Is this your goal?  I mean this is what Paul lays out to the Colossians as the ultimate goal.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Your whole life is to please God?  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There is no more of you and your desires\'85it is all about Him and what He wants for you!\
\pard\pardeftab720\li360\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs28 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Is the goal of your life to please God or you?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 bearing fruit in every good work, growing in the knowledge of God,\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There is a tie here\'85as they bear good fruit in their life their knowledge of God grows.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In many ways it is circular.  As you grow in the knowledge of God about how he created you and how He calls you to live you are able to live that out and in turn you will grow deeper in your knowledge of God.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Knowledge of God, as we will see, is not book knowledge.  It isn\'92t going to church and learning Bible stories about David and Goliath.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is spiritual and deeper than that.  It is revealed in those stories but not those stories (need to flesh this out more I think)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 11\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub being strengthened with all power\'a0according to his glorious might so that you may have great endurance and patience,\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls13\ilvl0\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There is the generic standards we all have and the unique calling we each have\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So the first step is to understand the unique things that are spiritual that God is calling you too\'85but there is a catch!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The things that God will call you too will force you to rely and run towards Him because you will know you can\'92t do it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}That as we understand and go deeper into our relationship with God we should also naturally and instinctively be forced into a deeper trust relationship with God.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can\'92t have one without the other.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The tension though is it becomes very clear in this passage that without God\'92s power in your life you are unable to live the life He has called you to.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls14\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs28 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When was the last time you hit your knee\'92s in prayer because the call on your life was too big without Him?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls14\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92re not talking about nice safe Christianity here.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 12\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub and giving joyful thanks to the Father,\'a0who has qualified you
\fs15 \super [\ul f\ulnone ]
\fs24 \nosupersub \'a0to share in the inheritance\'a0of his holy people in the kingdom of light.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls15\ilvl0\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This next part is why an understanding of the Gospel is so important\'85because Paul makes this statement that you have been qualified to \'91share in the inheritance\'92 of God\'92s people in the \'91kingdom of light\'92.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The biggest issue for most Christians isn\'92t how do I have better marriages or get a better job or have better kids\'85the number thing I deal with Christians about at it\'92s core is \'93How do I know if I\'92m saved\'94.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Can I lose my salvation and what are the sins that can do it?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So Paul tells a group of people he has never met but that have been saved\'85you\'92re qualified.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He has no clue their past, present, or future\'85but he is confident that they are qualified to get into this new kingdom of light.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Now Paul is about unpack the main part of this whole book and why we come together as a church every week\'85\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls15\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs28 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Last Question \'96 Are you truly saved?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls15\ilvl1
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Is it is about you or not?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Do you have conviction or nothing?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What propels you in life?  Hope in now or later?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Where are you REALLY with God?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs36 \cf0 CONCLUSION\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls16\ilvl0
\f3\b0\fs28 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Wrap up with salvation moment and opportunity to walk back with others.\
}